parameters.name: 12恋愛パート・お洒落・落ち着いた

parameters: Pony-Celes: "Hold on tight, are you okay...?"
Pony-Celes: "It seems you've come to. Can you walk?"

Karen: (Eh... what's this? I can see Pony-Celes and Morisaki
overlapping...)

Karen: (No way, that can't be true... Is Pony-Celes actually
Morisaki!?)

Karen: "...I appreciate that you helped me. But don't touch me so
casually!"

Pony-Celes: (Ugh, really, what's with her. This is why I have
trouble with Ms. Saionji...)
Karen: "You look like you want to say something."
Pony-Celes: "No... If you're that lively, then you must be fine."
Karen: "Don't get cocky just because you helped me, Morisaki!!"
Karen: "An idiot doesn't change just by changing appearances..."
